{"tid":1361762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚所有醫護/專職醫療撚!!!! 強烈譴責 「香港護士總工會」及「香港政府華員會護士分會」","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:17:07.000Z","uid":190854,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"57ed6a099e0b7b7eb52d49d6b032050ca8b296c5","tid":1361762,"uid":190854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"如果方便的話拜託share一下, 謝謝!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewRhKRAhIeirRO4pl_gJGgLqEL8AkpIzVjZKw9eon0KN2UaA/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSewRhKRAhIeirRO4pl_gJGgLqEL8AkpIzVjZKw9eon0KN2UaA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0BYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=db9f2a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewRhKRAhIeirRO4pl_gJGgLqEL8AkpIzVjZKw9eon0KN2UaA/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n尋日 唔少醫院既ward都收到呢兩個唔春知咩離地紅底老屎忽工會既mass fax <br />\n仲有附件show哂當事人既所有資料同posting出黎<br />\n<br />\n同業post既字眼可能有問題<br />\n但而家幾時變到工會有權以言入罪 做政治審查同公審批鬥？<br />\n作為所謂工會<br />\n此等處理手法極唔恰當<br />\n我唔識當事人<br />\n但我真心好嬲<br />\n呢個時勢都仲要咁樣玩horizontal violence去搞自己人<br />\n希望大家簽一簽!! 唔好比班\b垃圾老屎忽玩玩割蓆搞自己人!!<br />\n<br />\n可以的話請forward, 醫生護士PT OT ST MSW Radi Optom RD Podi CP等等乜professional都可以聲援!<br />\n<br />\n感謝!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQfqOD5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQfqOD5.png&h=57feac11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNyG6qM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNyG6qM.png&h=5d4c2804&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frmafi7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffrmafi7.png&h=02028c24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5c24543111b8cf8b67c4b654ee9e892e2b697b0","tid":1361762,"uid":190854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"Pish